<item>
  <title>정규 분포</title>
  <link>https://cryscham123.github.io/posts/phd_statistics/6-정규분포.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p><img src="https://cryscham123.github.io/img/stat-thumb.jpg" class="post-thumbnail img-fluid"></p>
<section id="linear-transformation" class="level1">
<h1>Linear Transformation</h1>
<section id="정규-분포의-합" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="정규-분포의-합">정규 분포의 합</h2>
<p>두 분포의 합이 같은 분포가 되는 경우는 흔치 않다 (uniform distribution도 같지 않다)</p>
<p>두 정규분포의 합은 정규분포가 된다</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?X%20+%20Y%20%5Csim%20N(%CE%BC_1%20+%20%CE%BC_2,%20%CF%83_1%5E2%20+%20%CF%83_2%5E2)"></p>
</section>
<section id="chi-square-분포" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="chi-square-분포">Chi-square 분포</h2>
<p>α = ν/2, θ = 2인 감마분포</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?Z%20%5Csim%20N(0,1)">일 때, <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?Z%5E2%20%5Csim%20%CF%87%5E2(1)"></p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?Z_i%20%5Csim%20N(0,1)">일 때, <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?Z_1%5E2%20+%20Z_2%5E2%20+%20...%20%20+%20Z_n%5E2%20%5Csim%20%CF%87%5E2(n)"></p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?X_i">가 서로 독립이고, 자유도가 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%CE%BD_i">인 카이제곱분포를 따른다면, <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?X_1%20+%20X_2%20+%20...%20+%20X_n%20%5Csim%20x%5E2(%CE%BD_1%20+%20%CE%BD_2%20+%20...%20+%20%CE%BD_n)"></p>


</section>
</section>

