  <title>확률변수의 기댓값</title>
  <link>https://cryscham123.github.io/posts/phd_statistics/3-확률변수의-기댓값.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p><img src="https://cryscham123.github.io/img/stat-thumb.jpg" class="post-thumbnail img-fluid"></p>
<section id="확률변수의-기댓값" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="확률변수의-기댓값">확률변수의 기댓값</h2>
<ul>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%CE%BC%20=%20E(x)">로 가정. (모집단)</p></li>
<li><p>covariance는 선형관계를 보여준다.<br>
<code>x와 y는 독립이다 -&gt; cov(x, y) = 0</code></p></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="moment-generationg-functions" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="moment-generationg-functions">Moment Generationg Functions</h2>
<ul>
<li>평균과 분산만으로 확률분포를 설명하기에는 부족하다.<br>
</li>
<li>moment: <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%CE%BC_k%E2%80%B2%20=%20E(X%5Ek),%20k%20%E2%88%88%20%E2%84%A4+"></li>
<li>Var(x) = <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%CE%BC_2%E2%80%B2%20-%20%CE%BC_1%E2%80%B2%5E2"></li>
<li>E(x) = <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%CE%BC_1%E2%80%B2"></li>
<li>모든 k에 대해 검증 불가 =&gt; mgf(moment generating function)</li>
<li>mgf: <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?M_X(t)%20=%20E(e%5E%7Btx%7D)"></li>
</ul>
<ol type="1">
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?M_X(t)%20=%201%20+%20t%CE%BC_1%E2%80%B2%20+%20%5Cfrac%7Bt%5E2%7D%7B2!%7D%CE%BC_2%E2%80%B2%20+%20%5Cfrac%7Bt%5E3%7D%7B3!%7D%CE%BC_3%E2%80%B2%20+%20..."></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?M%E2%80%B2(t)%20=%20%CE%BC_1%E2%80%B2%20+%20%5Cfrac%7B2t%7D%7B2!%7D%CE%BC_2%E2%80%B2%20+%20%5Cfrac%7B3t%5E2%7D%7B3!%7D%CE%BC_3%E2%80%B2%20+%20..."></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?M%E2%80%B2(0)%20=%20%CE%BC_1%E2%80%B2"></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?M%E2%80%B2%E2%80%B2(0)%20=%20%CE%BC_2%E2%80%B2"></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?M%5E%7B(k)%7D(0)%20=%20%CE%BC_k%E2%80%B2"></p></li>
</ol>


</section>

